948423759.text: "This etoposide induced hyperphosphorylation of Mre11 and Nbs1 in L2A (-) cells was prevented using caffeine or an ATR specific inhibitor but not ATM or Chk1 inhibitors (XREF_FIG), suggesting a possible disruption of the Chk1-ATR regulatory circuit upon CMA blockage that results in abnormal ATR dependent phosphorylation of MRN proteins."
